# i18n keys

`[DOMAIN]_[ENTITY]_[CONTEXT]_[MODIFIER]` — DOMAIN/ENTITY PascalCase; CONTEXT/MODIFIER snake_case.

Examples: `Facility_mgmt`, `Facility_Name`, `Announcement_created`, `Edit_Pricing_Rule`, `*_descr`.

Update all locales; no camelCase keys; no generic `name` when prefixed key exists.
